{"article_id":"PGLqDyyEGR83E6Qb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"More Arrests Possible In The Killing Of Ahmaud Arbery , Georgia Investigators Say","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"On what would have been Ahmaud Arbery 's 26th birthday ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"Georgia state authorities said Friday","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"that more arrests are possible in the shooting death of the black jogger","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"who was killed","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"while unarmed in February in the Satilla Shores neighborhood in Glynn County , Ga .","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"The director of the Georgia Bureau of Investigation , Vic Reynolds , also shed light on his department 's swift decision","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to arrest two white men , a father and son , in connection with Arbery 's killing ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"two days after taking over the investigation from local authorities .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"On Thursday , Gregory McMichael , 64 , and his son Travis , 34 , were charged with murder and aggravated assault .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"The McMichaels are being held in the Glynn County Jail ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"according to a GBI press release .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Gregory McMichael is a former investigator with a local district attorney 's office .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"When asked about additional arrests ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Reynolds replied ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"`` Do n't know yet .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"We 're going to go","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"wherever the evidence takes us . ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Cellphone video","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"posted online earlier this week ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"which appeared to capture Arbery 's Feb. 23 death ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"sparked national outcry and calls for arrests .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` We 're investigating everyone involved in the case , including the individual","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who shot the video , ''","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Reynolds said .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"In a phone interview with Fox News on Friday , President Trump was asked about that case ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"which he called a `` very sad thing . ''","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"`` It 's a very disturbing situation to me ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and I just ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"you know ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"my heart goes out to the parents and the family and the friends , ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"`` To anybody","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that watched it ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"certainly it was a disturbing or troubling video ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"no question about that , ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"he said ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"adding :","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"`` It 's a sad thing , very sad thing .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Hate to see that . ''","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"The Thursday evening arrests of the McMichaels ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"who have said","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"they were acting in self-defense ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"caps off several days of rapid developments in the Arbery case .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"It had stalled for more than two months","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"with no charges filed .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Two district attorneys had recused themselves from the case .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"On May 5 ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"after the video was released ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Atlantic Judicial Circuit District Attorney Tom Durden requested GBI investigate the Arbery death .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"The local police department also asked for assistance from state authorities .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Reynolds said during the press conference","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"that agents pored over the investigative file","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"compiled by the local authorities","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"most of the day on Wednesday .","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"By about 5 p.m. Thursday ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Reynolds said","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"his agents `` had established sufficient probable cause","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"to seek arrest warrants '' against the McMichaels .","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"When asked what his department saw in the case file","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that local authorities might have missed ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Reynolds said ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"`` I ca n't answer what another agency did or did n't see . ''","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"`` But I can tell you","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"that","depth":16},{"id":65,"text":"based on our involvement in this case ,","depth":17},{"id":66,"text":"considering the fact","depth":18},{"id":67,"text":"that we hit the ground running Wednesday morning ,","depth":18},{"id":68,"text":"within 36 hours , we had secured warrants for two individuals for felony murder .","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"I think","depth":16},{"id":70,"text":"that speaks volumes for itself","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"and that the probable cause was clear to our agents pretty quickly . ''","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"Following the McMichaels ' arrests Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"family attorney Benjamin Crump tweeted ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"`` it took 74 days","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"but Ahmaud Arbery 's killers have finally been arrested ! ''","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Gregory McMichael told police","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"that there had been several recent break-ins in the neighborhood","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"and that","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"while in his front yard ,","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"he saw the person","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"he suspected from those incidents","depth":17},{"id":82,"text":"`` hauling ass '' down Satilla Drive toward Burford Drive ,","depth":16},{"id":83,"text":"according to a Feb. 23 Glynn County Police Department incident report .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"The McMichaels hopped in a truck with guns ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"the older McMichael with a .357 Magnum and Travis a shotgun ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"the report states .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"When they eventually caught up to Arbery ,","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"the younger McMichael exited the truck with his shotgun ,","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"and that 's when the `` unidentified male began to violently attack Travis ''","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"and the two men began fighting over the gun ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"the McMichael 's statement to police said .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"The facts of what is publicly known about the case are somewhat clear ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Georgia Public Broadcasting 's Emily Jones said Friday on Morning Edition .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"`` As for why this may have taken so long ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Gregory McMichael has worked in law enforcement in the area for more than 20 years ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"including time","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"working as an investigator in the district attorney 's office in Brunswick , ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Jones said .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Arbery 's family has characterized his death as a modern-day lynching .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"His aunt , Thea Brooks , told GPB News","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"even though the community is celebrating the arrests ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"there is a long way to go","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"before the case is resolved .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"`` This is only the beginning , ''","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"`` We still got ta wait for the conviction .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"This is just the start . ''","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"NAACP President Derrick Johnson said during a Friday afternoon media briefing","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"that the Arbery shooting represents just the latest in an `` ongoing , systemic attack on African Americans '' by law enforcement and vigilantes .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"`` The sad part of this , ''","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Johnson said ,","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"`` is these attackers felt","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that they were within their right of white privilege","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"and protected by the color of law","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"because one of them happened to be a former law enforcement officer . ''","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"At the press conference , Reynolds , the GBI director , was asked","depth":3},{"id":118,"text":"whether there was enough evidence","depth":4},{"id":119,"text":"to charge the McMichaels with a hate crime .","depth":4},{"id":120,"text":"Georgia is one of four states , along with Wyoming , Arkansas and South Carolina ,","depth":3},{"id":121,"text":"that do n't have hate crime laws on the books","depth":4},{"id":122,"text":"and do n't require officials collect data on hate crimes ,","depth":4},{"id":123,"text":"according to the U.S. Department of Justice .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":247,"left":243,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":240,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":163,"right":239,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":148,"right":162,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":136,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":129,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":0,"right":128,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":1,"right":127,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":2,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity"